<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<pb n="0214a" xml:id="I01.0079.0214a" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0214a01"/><cb:docNumber>No. 79</cb:docNumber>
<lb ed="I" n="0214a02"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"></cb:mulu><cb:jhead><title>王氏道俗百人造像記</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<pb n="0215a" xml:id="I01.0079.0215a" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0215a01"/><p cb:type="pre" xml:id="pI01p0215a0101">夫玄籍理融。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">妙</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">出</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">淨</unclear>言之表。□□□窮。可聞難睹。四□覆育。普救□物。出沒自由。神變自<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">在</unclear>．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0215a02"/><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">而</unclear>名□時。有大比丘僧法師。累行積因。塵劫餘□□□□□背塵境。合寺僧眾。威儀逮〃．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0215a03"/>名經披攬。演法未聞。隨機頓漸。逕救講寺。契．．．．．．．利。帶浮自守。應託閻浮。人．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0215a04"/>四葳齊等。宿□德本。又是大士。能以不足．．．．．．．．．已抽有愍愚<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">愛</unclear>智．．．率契．．<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">道</unclear>
<lb ed="I" n="0215a05"/>俗一百人等。時以王氏。磐根太原。海內<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">君</unclear>．．．．．．．．．．積善空王。高鑒自<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0215001" n="0215001"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0215001" n="0215001"/><anchor xml:id="beg0215001" n="0215001"/>遠<anchor xml:id="end0215001"/>。里人若歸．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0215a06"/>中白玉石像一區。舉高一仞。釋迦當陽。．．．．．．．．．．<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">藥</unclear>王。文殊。維摩大士。乃<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">重</unclear>．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0215a07"/>天人散華。無事不有。菩薩乘空。百．．．．．．．．．．．．頂禮。世謂<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0215002" n="0215002"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0215002" n="0215002"/><anchor xml:id="beg0215002" n="0215002"/>希<anchor xml:id="end0215002"/>奇。此土未有。道俗．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0215a08"/>可因此福力之<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">冥</unclear>。上為皇帝．．．．．．．．．．．．．．方太然。干戈不起。龍雨順時。□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">涂</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">常</unclear>□
<lb ed="I" n="0215a09"/>土豐民寧。歸依正道。．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．海望<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0215003" n="0215003"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0215003" n="0215003"/><anchor xml:id="beg0215003" n="0215003"/>英<anchor xml:id="end0215003"/>儒。標心悟解。上為七祖先<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">靈</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">永</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">別</unclear>
<lb ed="I" n="0215a10"/>苦因。超昇淨土。合邑．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．官<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">持</unclear>寵。現在常安。不乏財有。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">所</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">同</unclear>述<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">心</unclear>□□
<lb ed="I" n="0215a11"/>遐壽。眷屬康延。<anchor xml:id="beg_1" type="star"/>遠<anchor xml:id="end_1"/>塵離□□蠢．．．．．．．．．．．大齊河清三年二月八日合邑義□．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0215a12"/>靈碁磻礡。神冑淵玄。河．．．．．．．．．．．．．天豪□七<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0215004" n="0215004"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0215004" n="0215004"/><anchor xml:id="beg0215004" n="0215004"/>冏<anchor xml:id="end0215004"/>八相。花□如．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0215a13"/>獨朗。秋蓮　　綿綿。．．．．．．．．．．擾四生。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">循</unclear>環□□。往返難平。大覺翻．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0215a14"/>□榮。人天盛顯。地獄流明。□□河□客茲．．．．．．．．．．隨波遷寶隱<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">洛</unclear>．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0215a15"/>簪依佛。出離埃塵。青蓮比<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">淨</unclear>．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．德合境稱<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">尊</unclear>．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0215a16"/>志在道門。五教敷慧。．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．恒居一．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0215a17"/>紀。思念菩提。長．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．永傳名諱．．．
<lb ed="I" n="0215a18"/>．．<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">堪</unclear><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">佛</unclear>主<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">王</unclear>．．．</p></cb:div>
